| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-1090 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: c802f031-bcdb-5d7a-acc8-236ae79f1b04"
